name: Annika Mossberg
coverLetter: I trimmed for one season of outdoor in California earlier this fall, and am comfortable trimming a variety of strains. I just moved to Portland so I have a flexible schedule and am able to work full-time, part-time, or seasonally. I am easy to work with, and am a hard worker. I am enthusiastic and knowledgeable about cannabis, and am always interested in learning more about the industry.
